OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV News: a new but familiar look
OL,4,
OL,5,FThe revamp of STV News looks good but
OL,6,Fis hardly worth the hyperbole of some
OL,7,Fclickbait articles.
OL,9,FIt is a simple evolution of the look of
OL,10,Fthe programme.
OL,12,FIts last significant visual overhaul
OL,13,Fwas 10 years ago. Time alone means it
OL,14,Fis now time to freshen things up.
OL,16,FEverything changes but everything
OL,17,Fremains the same.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
