OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV News: a new but familiar look
OL,4,
OL,5,FThe new set is still a very similar
OL,6,Fshade of blue. The signature tune has
OL,7,Fonly been remixed slightly.
OL,9,FThe format of the programme - revised
OL,10,Flast year when dual presentation from
OL,11,Fboth Glasgow and Edinburgh ended -
OL,12,Fremains the same.
OL,14,FThe advantage of the new set is that it
OL,15,Flooks more modern and allows more space
OL,16,Ffor reporters to join the presenter.
OL,18,FBut I bet 90% of viewers will hardly
OL,19,Fnotice the changes in a couple of
OL,20,Fweeks. And this is how it should be.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
