OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV News: a new but familiar look
OL,4,
OL,5,FThe days when regional news programmes
OL,6,Fgot brand new looks every two or three
OL,7,Fyears are thankfully gone.
OL,9,FNew looks always brought complaints -
OL,10,Fsome viewers simply disliked the
OL,11,Funfamiliarity.
OL,13,FThe STV News at 6 is a successful
OL,14,Fprogramme. The challenge was to build a
OL,15,Fnew set, refresh the graphics and
OL,16,Fpotentially enhance the programme
OL,17,Fwithout annoying loyal viewers.
OL,19,FThere have been no changes to the
OL,20,Fformat.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
