OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV News: a new but familiar look
OL,4,
OL,5,FI mentioned how many regional news
OL,6,Fprogrammes used to get new looks more
OL,7,Foften than weather presenters changed
OL,8,Ftheir hairstyle.
OL,10,FBy my reckoning there were five
OL,11,Fdistinct looks for what was then
OL,12,FScotland Today between 1986 and 1996.
OL,13,FEach change brought completely new
OL,14,Ftitles, music and sets plus alterations
OL,15,Fto the format.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
