OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV News: a new but familiar look
OL,4,
OL,5,FIn contrast News at Ten stayed
OL,6,Ffundamentally unchanged from 1967 to
OL,7,F1992. Each new look kept the core
OL,8,Felements and format, simply freshening
OL,9,Fup the appearance and taking advantage
OL,10,Fof new technology.
OL,12,FThere is no suggestion of any change to
OL,13,Fthe format of STV News soon.
OL,15,FDropping the Edinburgh sub-opt would
OL,16,Fneed Ofcom approval.
OL,18,FSo would fundamental changes like an
OL,19,Fend to the separate programme for the
OL,20,Fformer Grampian region.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
