OL,4,
OL,5,FWhether they'd ever dare to record this
OL,6,Fin Glasgow at 5pm - aping some English
OL,7,Fregions - is another question.
OL,9,FSo, all in all it's an attractive new
OL,10,Flook but one which will quickly become
OL,11,Fvery familiar.
